{"tid":1522992,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我好熱","createTime":"2019-08-31T15:09:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T05:44:29.000Z","uid":238801,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5db1623aaff81f0daa2c484f5555bb187bf10316","tid":1522992,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:09:42.000Z","msg":"嗌到好熱<br />\n今日真係好多嘢想講<br />\n好想resign<br />\n唔係因為我係死廢青頂唔順<br />\n係因為我全部同事都係港豬<br />\n第一次感受到咩叫恥與為伍<br />\n雖然我都只係和理非唔敢上前線做勇武<br />\n但我真係第一次見識到有人係可以淨係關心自己有冇車番到屋企<br />\n搭地鐵見到勇武手足行入嚟佢竟然叫我企過另一邊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我覺得好恥辱 一路搭車一路覺得好撚慚愧羞恥<br />\n不過好彩岩岩番到屋企大嗌咗一粒鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家心情舒服番啲<br />\n同埋應該點開口話想唔做<br />\n利申岩岩番左一個禮拜....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48ef50270e4a97e163d89538885b6a8bcaf12e3d","tid":1522992,"uid":238801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:10:46.000Z","msg":"完全feel到自己同嗰度啲人係兩種生物嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我屌 好撚想辭職啊"},{"pid":"d43b6a4c5f3e630bb7011c86e9cce1a8ebcc08aa","tid":1522992,"uid":140549,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:11:49.000Z","msg":"如果唔係好好pay就走啦 遲早有日你會頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a354914a10be7657b2c1f9cd59344e31f1ca839","tid":1522992,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d43b6a4c5f3e630bb7011c86e9cce1a8ebcc08aa","tid":1522992,"uid":140549,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:11:49.000Z","msg":"如果唔係好好pay就走啦 遲早有日你會頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:14:18.000Z","msg":"超級唔好pay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />on撚9"},{